---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<!-- Astro -->
<Layout
  title="Frequently Asked Questions | MWRS"
  description="Answers to common questions about counseling, medication management, insurance, telehealth, and getting started with care at Mental Wellness & Relationship Services (MWRS)."
>
    <main class="faq-page">
        <!-- Hero / intro -->
        <section class="faq-hero">
            <div class="faq-hero-inner">
                <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
                <p>
                    Here are a few common questions about counseling, medication
                    management, and getting started at Mental Wellness &amp;
                    Relationship Services (MWRS). If you don’t see your question
                    here, you’re always welcome to reach out directly.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- FAQ list -->
        <section class="faq-list-section">
            <div class="faq-list-inner">
                <!-- Item 1 -->
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary class="faq-question">
                        How do I get started with counseling or medication care?
                    </summary>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            The simplest way is to fill out our
                            <a href="/contact-us"
                                >Start Counseling or Medication Care</a
                            >
                            form. Our intake team will review your information,
                            check availability, and contact you to discuss next steps
                            and scheduling.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </details>

                <!-- FAQ Item #2 – Insurance -->
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary class="faq-question">
                        What insurance plans do you accept?
                    </summary>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            We work with a wide range of insurance providers.
                            Below is our current list:
                        </p>

                        <div class="insurance-grid">
                            <ul>
                                <li>Cash Pay</li>
                                <li>Aetna</li>
                                <li>Blue Cross of Idaho</li>
                                <li>BPA EAP</li>
                                <li>Champ VA</li>
                                <li>Cigna/Evernorth</li>
                                <li>Curalinc EAP</li>
                                <li>First Choice</li>
                                <li>GPA</li>
                                <li>Humana</li>
                                <li>Kaiser</li>
                                <li>Magellan</li>
                            </ul>

                            <ul>
                                <li>Medicaid (Idaho)</li>
                                <li>Medicare</li>
                                <li>Molina of Idaho</li>
                                <li>New Directions EAP</li>
                                <li>Optum</li>
                                <li>Pacific Source</li>
                                <li>Premera Blue Cross</li>
                                <li>Regence BCBS (Any State)</li>
                                <li>TriCare West</li>
                                <li>TriWest / VA</li>
                                <li>United Healthcare (UHC)</li>
                                <li>Vital EAP</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </details>

                <!-- Item 3 -->
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary class="faq-question">
                        Which locations offer in-person appointments?
                    </summary>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            We currently offer in-person counseling in Coeur
                            d’Alene, Ponderay, Priest River, and Oldtown.
                            Medication management is available in Coeur d’Alene,
                            Ponderay, and via telehealth.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            You can see a full overview of our offices on the
                            <a href="/locations">Locations</a> page.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </details>

                <!-- Item 5 -->
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary class="faq-question">
                        Can I see the same provider for both counseling and
                        medication?
                    </summary>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            In most cases, counseling and medication management
                            are provided by different clinicians on the same
                            team. Your counselor and nurse practitioner can
                            coordinate care as appropriate so that your
                            treatment plan feels cohesive and focused on your
                            goals.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </details>

                <!-- Item 6 -->
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary class="faq-question">
                        Do you work with teens and children?
                    </summary>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            Yes. Several of our counselors work with teens, and
                            some providers see children depending on age and
                            clinical fit. When you complete the intake form, let
                            us know your child’s age and what you’re hoping to
                            work on so we can match you with an appropriate
                            clinician.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </details>

                <!-- Item 7 -->
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary class="faq-question">
                        What if I’m not sure whether I need counseling,
                        medication, or both?
                    </summary>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            That’s very common. On our
                            <a href="/contact-us"
                                >Start Counseling or Medication Care</a
                            >
                            form you can select “I’m not sure / both.” Our team
                            will review your responses and may recommend starting
                            with counseling, a medication consultation, or a combination
                            depending on your symptoms and preferences.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </details>

                <!-- Item 8 -->
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary class="faq-question">
                        What should I expect in my first appointment?
                    </summary>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            The first visit is mostly about getting to know you.
                            Your provider will ask about your concerns, history,
                            and what you hope to change. You are always welcome
                            to move at your own pace, and you do not have to
                            share anything you’re not ready to talk about yet.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </details>

                <!-- Item 9 – Billing questions -->
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary class="faq-question">
                        What if I have questions about a bill?
                    </summary>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            If something on your statement doesn’t look right,
                            or you want help understanding a charge, our admin
                            team is happy to review it with you. You can send a
                            quick billing message through our secure online
                            form.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <a href="/billing#billing-questions" class="faq-link">
                                Go to Billing & Payments →
                            </a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </details>

                <!-- Item X – Sliding Fee Discount Program -->
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary class="faq-question">
                        Do you offer a Sliding Fee Discount Program?
                    </summary>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            Yes. MWRS offers a Sliding Fee Discount Program for
                            clients who qualify based on household size and
                            income. If you’d like details or want to request an
                            application, you can use the brief form on our
                            <a href="/services#sliding-fee">Services page</a>.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            The form only asks for basic contact information and
                            lets our team follow up with the exact steps and
                            documentation you may need.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </details>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <style>
        .faq-page {
            background: #e5e9f3;
            min-height: 100vh;
                  background-image: url("/images/paper-texture.png");
      background-repeat: repeat; /* tile it */
      background-size: 420px 420px; /* tweak smaller/larger as you like */
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
        }

        .faq-hero {
            padding: 10rem 1.5rem 3.5rem;
            background: #fbfbf9;
                  background-image: url("/images/paper-texture.png");
      background-repeat: repeat; /* tile it */
      background-size: 420px 420px; /* tweak smaller/larger as you like */
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
        }

        .faq-hero-inner {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .faq-hero h1 {
            font-family: "Belleza", sans-serif;
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
            letter-spacing: 0.16em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin: 0 0 1rem;
            color: #111827;
        }

        .faq-hero p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #4b5563;
        }

        .faq-list-section {
            padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem 4rem;
        }

        .faq-list-inner {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1.3rem;
        }

        .faq-item {
            border-radius: 20px;
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
            box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
            padding: 1.1rem 1.4rem;
        }

        .faq-item summary {
            list-style: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker {
            display: none;
        }

        .faq-question {
            font-size: 0.98rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #111827;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
        }

        /* Optional: small “+ / –” indicator using CSS only */
        .faq-item summary::after {
            content: "+";
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #6b7280;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            transition:
                transform 0.15s ease,
                color 0.15s ease;
        }

        .faq-item[open] summary::after {
            content: "–";
            color: #111827;
        }

        .faq-answer {
            margin-top: 0.6rem;
            font-size: 0.94rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #4b5563;
        }

        .faq-answer a {
            color: #111827;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .insurance-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.2rem;
            margin-top: 0.75rem;
        }

        .insurance-grid ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 1.2rem;
            color: #4b5563;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</Layout>